### Get all users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/
Authorization: Bearer admin_token_value_here

### Get users by location
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/location?region=Lagos&branch=HQ
Authorization: Bearer admin_token_value_here

### Get single user
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/695793ebcac261dff38180f5
Authorization: Bearer admin_token_value_here

### Get single user (UNAUTHORIZED - Regular user)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/695793ebcac261dff38180f5
Authorization: Bearer user_token_value_here